Healthcare Equipment and Supplies

Company Overview of Hemex Health, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Hemex Health, Inc. develops malaria and sickle cell diagnostic devices. It offers HEMECHIP, a device that identifies hemoglobin disorders. The company was founded in 2016 and is headquartered in Portland, Oregon.


154 NW Maywood DrivePortland, OR 97210United StatesFounded in 2016



Phone: 503-703-7696

hemexhealth.com







